A motorcyclist has died following a two-vehicle collision with a van, say police.The incident, involving a KTM Duke motorcycle and a black VW Transporter van, happened at about 14:30 BST on Saturday.The male rider was declared dead at the scene of the crash, which occurred on the A548 between Llangernyw and Llanfair Talhaiarn, Conwy county.North Wales Police has appealed for any witnesses to contact the force.
